---

<Layout
  title="Andres Lopez | Front-End Developer"
  description="Explore a showcase of my talents and projects, demonstrating expertise in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and more. Let's bring your digital vision to life together."
>
  <Section id="home">
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 w-screen min-h-screen lg:w-[950px] pt-28 px-10 lg:px-0"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
        <h1 class="my-5 text-3xl text-balance font-bold uppercase">
          Hello,<br />welcome to my portfolio!
        </h1>
        <p class="m-0 text-pretty">
          I'm a junior front-end developer based in Bogotá, Colombia, with a
          strong passion for creating functional and visually appealing
          websites. I am committed to expanding my skills and knowledge to
          provide the best possible solutions for each project, whether it
          involves creating new websites or maintaining existing ones.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col items-end justify-center">
        <img
          class="w-[350px] h-[350px] border-4 border-purple-800 rounded-full object-cover object-top"
          src="/profile.jpg"
          alt="Andres Lopez"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
  <Section id="experience">
    <h1 class="my-5 text-3xl text-balance font-bold uppercase">Experience</h1>
    <ExperienceCard
      title="Freelancer"
      date="2022 - Current"
      location="Bogotá, Colombia"
    >
      As a freelance web developer, I have gained extensive experience creating
      stunning websites using WordPress and Elementor. From client projects to
      personal ventures, I have utilized these technologies to deliver visually
      appealing and functional websites. With a focus on user experience and
      responsiveness, I ensure each site I create meets the needs of both
      clients and users.
    </ExperienceCard>
  </Section>
  <Section id="projects">
    <h1 class="my-5 text-3xl text-balance font-bold uppercase">
      Know my projects
    </h1>
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 justify-center w-full lg:w-[900px] gap-12 lg:my-6 p-14 lg:p-0"
    >
      <ProjectCard
        title="clinica-de-obesidad"
        technologies="WordPress, Elementor"
        liveURL="https://clinicadeobesidad.andreslopez.co/"
      />
      <ProjectCard
        title="credit-card-simulator"
        technologies="HTML, CSS, JavaScript"
        liveURL="https://creditcardsimulator.andreslopez.co/"
      />
    </div>
  </Section>
